What this does:
When you use UITableViews and you click a cell: 
  - show an indicator in the accessoryType
  - show the NetworkActivityIndicator
  - Disable clicking of the button
  - Call didSelectRowAtIndexPath:(NSIndexPath *)indexPath inBackground:(Boolean)background;
  - Reset everything

Using categories from a library with iPhone: http://developer.apple.com/library/mac/#qa/qa2006/qa1490.html
Use the "Other linker flags" option: -all_load